//creating a deployment descriptor file (web.xml)
-------------------------------------------------
<web-app>
<servlet>
   <servlet-name>First</servlet-name>
   <servlet-class>test.WelcomeServlet</servlet-class>
</servlet>

<servlet-mapping>
    <servlet-name>First</servlet-name>
    <url-pattern>/welcome</url-pattern>
</servlet-mapping>
</web-app>

What is the purpose of deployment descriptor (web.xml) file?
-->To map servlet to the particular URL.
